Package jetbrains.mps.persistence

Class ByteArrayInputSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • jetbrains.mps.persistence.StreamDataSourceBase
      • jetbrains.mps.persistence.ByteArrayInputSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StreamAsMultiDataSource, DataSource, MultiStreamDataSource, StreamDataSource
    public final class ByteArrayInputSource
extends StreamDataSourceBase
    Bare input source for models backed by plain byte array. Doesn't dispatch events (nor track listeners), doesn't manage timestamp. input stream could be open multiple times.
    Since:
    3.4
